race.description: Horsepower Feeds & Supplements Super Maiden Hcp
race.comment: IMPURITEZE (4) back in good order after she raced on the speed for a tenacious second over 1200m at Gosford. McMurray keeps the ride and no surprise to see her put this field away. RESUME (13) big improver at her second run back when caught the eye to secure third over 1300m at Wyong. Expect to see her a little closer in the run and shapes as a genuine top-three player. MARK OF GLORY (15) chipped away late on debut when a plugging fifth over 1200m at Gosford. Since fitted with a 1050m tick over trial at Randwick. Improver over this trip. ASILAH (7) Wootton Bassett filly from Group 2 winning mare I'll Have A Bit on debut for the Waller yard. Finished close up in her last two trials and not to be overlooked.
